title: BabySleepBot
description: Teach your baby to sleep through the night and take longer naps! Jennifer Duff, Australia's top rated baby sleep consultant, transforms her 22 years of experience into easy to follow steps, showing you exactly what to do in less than 1 hour! Listen to bite-sized audio clips, and in your corner - the magic of BabySleepBot, your own AI chatbot assistant trained by Jennifer to answer all your questions instantly, even through the night!
